reviewText:
As a beginning archer, I enjoyed this video. It has a lot of great insight from talented barebow archers. Each segment is on a different archer and a particular aspect of their shot process. Each having their own particular style, it's a great way to learn about different techniques and experiment it within your own shot process.

The production quality is a bit dated but still professionally done. Audio is clear and video is good .
It's all the greats telling you how they get it done. What's not to like?
